# Return & Refund System

A web-based Return & Refund Management System that allows customers to submit, track, and manage product return requests. This system provides an admin and customer interface using JSP, Servlets, JSTL, and a MySQL database.

## 🧾 Features

- Customer login/logout
- Submit new return requests
- Filter returns by date and status
- Toggle between card and table view
- Track refund status
- Cancel pending requests
- Admin management (optional extension)

## 📁 Project Structure

```
